# Production build-time config (read automatically by `vite build`).
# This is a PUBLIC API endpoint, not a secret — it is embedded in the client
# bundle and visible in every browser request, so committing it is safe and
# makes production builds reproducible. A Vercel dashboard env var of the same
# name still takes precedence over this file if set.
VITE_API_BASE_URL=https://ioms-backend-kjvj.onrender.com
